des: Listen to the latest sermons from Wesley Memorial Church! You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to podcasts you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next". For more info on Wesley Memorial Church, visit wesleymemorial.org.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
